			<description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Company Overview</strong><br />Headquartered in Atlanta, Georgia, we are a  privately-held technology company specialized in providing unlimited  music downloads to thousands of users world-wide.  Our team is made up  of highly motivated, hard-working, and dynamic individuals. If you are  the type of person who is looking for a fast-paced, exciting, and  challenging position, you have found the right job.</p>
<p><strong>Job Description</strong><br />We  are looking for a full-time Promotional &amp; Customer Service  Specialist to help build a passionate following of online users around  our social media marketing platform and to provide friendly &amp;  helpful support to our current and potential customers.</p>
<p><strong>Job Responsibilities </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Answer customer inquiries via phone, email, &amp; live chat.</li>
<li>Manage our customer feedback &amp; support system via our online helpdesk system.</li>
<li>Create new marketing material, including but not limited to email campaigns, blog postings and special online contest.</li>
<li>Help build and manage our customer support knowledge base &amp; tutorial sections.</li>
<li>Manage relations with our merchant account provider to reduce charge-back rates.</li>
<li>Engage with customers via social media networks.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>What We Are Looking For </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Passion for providing outstanding customer service &amp; community management.</li>
<li>Superior organizational skills and attention to detail.</li>
<li>Outstanding communication skills.</li>
<li>Intelligent, hard-working, self-motivated, fun-loving individual.</li>
<li>Creative thinker.</li>
<li>Aptitude for understanding technology.</li>
<li>Understanding of social media.</li>
<li>Active energy level; Must maintain productivity in a fast paced environment.</li>
<li>Ability to work and make decisions with minimal supervision.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Compensation </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Ranging $8 per hour to $15 per hour based on experience.</li>
<li>Weekly payroll.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Hours</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Full-time from 10AM - 6PM, Monday thru Friday.</li>
<li>Part-time from 1PM - 5PM, Monday thru Friday.</li>
<li>Telecommuting will be considered.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Apply</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Email resume along with contact information. Interviews will begin in mid-August.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
